      • FTPStorageBucket

        public FTPStorageBucket(java.lang.String name,
                        java.lang.String user,
                        java.lang.String password,
                        java.lang.String host,
                        int port)
        Constructs a new storage bucket with the given properties.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of this buckes (also referred as id).
        user - the user name to authenticate in the FTP server.
        password - the password to to authenticate in the FTP server.
        host - the host (domain or ip address) of the FTP server.
        port - the port at which the server is listening.
